{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1624532724.643906", "card_id": "Q_466521697", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 408}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待欧洲宇航员正在紧锣密鼓地学习中文？中国的空间站还有哪些信息应当重点关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "中国空间站会邀请他国宇航员入住吗？答案是肯定的！ 根据欧洲空间局与中国航天局 2015 年达成的合作协议，双方将持续互派航天员进行综合性训练，目标是从 2022 年起开始让欧洲的航天员登上中国空间站。目前，来自德国、法国和意大利的三位航天员，已经在紧锣密鼓地学习中文，期待未来与中国同行进行流畅的合作。（人民日报微博）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-b9eaf871df8e4b7178ffe20c0e0c86d8_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "3932 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/466521697"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI2rbm8raFm6RrEAMaCDY1OTUxMDk0IM3VxYYGMOQBOJ0XQAByCTQ2NjUyMTY5N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1624532724.6447518", "card_id": "Q_433616847", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 2171}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "小学的成绩有很大的欺骗性，到了初中就会有很多的学生掉队，是真的吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-b45094ba93b483efbc23a887bcf0572b_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "2621 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/433616847"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I2rbm8raFm6RrEAMaCDU4NjM4Mjk0ILODs/4FMGs4xl9AAXIJNDMzNjE2ODQ3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1624532724.6451848", "card_id": "Q_466839329", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 269}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待收废品的大叔画上千幅油画火了，从专业的水平来看大叔画的怎么样？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "斗门街道的一条小巷里，一处寂静的低矮门楣，这几日突然热闹了起来。收了十几年废品的位光明，万万没想到，他火了，连同他的上千幅画作。现实版陋室铭！收废品大叔画上千幅油画，火了"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-dcd13b1a8fa31776e84fff50824190d6_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "2077 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#